xenserver

This module provides some puppetized sexy on xenserver systems

It incorporates automatic backups to disk of VMs on this system. Those backup scripts evolved [From scripts originated by Andy Burton](http://www.andy-burton.co.uk/blog/index.php/2009-11/updated-citrix-xenserver-5-5-automatic-vm-backup-scripts/)

